    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "E. L. PLUNKETT",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "Retired Capt. Brit. Army",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "October 26, 1952",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "Mr. I. H. Prahn",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "949 S. Jefferson Street,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "Franklin, Indiana.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "Dear Mr. Prahn:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "Once again I am happy to write to you about",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "IFSB and your fine work in helping our organization",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "grow larger and stronger.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "In your last letter you asked what course of action",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "your club should take in connection with IFSB. I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "would suggest the following:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "(1.) Appoint a local Chairman of the IFSB in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "Franklin, Indiana. Also appoint a local",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "treasurer and secretary.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "(2.) Hold your meetings at least twice a month,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "where you can discuss saucer happenings and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "club activities. Use a local hall, or better",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "yet, hold the meetings at each others homes.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "(3.) If and when you form your own city group, a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "certain portion of the club membership fee",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "may be retained by you to help your cause.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "(4.) Mr. Dick Campbell, is an International Officer",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "in IFSB and should be paid such respect at all",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "your gatherings.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "(5.) We will do any post card printing you desire,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "cards of similar size.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "(6.) You can print your club activities in \"Space",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "Review\".",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "(7.) Get contributions from your members to help",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "you get formed.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    }
